{"tid":2243071,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真討論］［拋磚引玉］最大型對外文宣行動- Save America","createTime":"2020-10-14T12:58:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T15:12:08.000Z","uid":302634,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d7df0caef7ee1e4e96a48bc913600d89aa27e1fd","tid":2243071,"uid":302634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T12:58:02.000Z","msg":"懶人包:<br />\n(香港時間)<br />\n14/10-19/10 集思廣益 達成共識<br />\n20/10-1/11 文宣製作(對內/外)<br />\n30/10- 4/11 對內文宣<br />\n3/11-4/11 美國總統選舉<br />\n4/11 晚上twitter對外文宣大行動<br />\n5/11 早上twitter對外文宣大行動<br />\n<br />\n美國大選將會喺3/11(美國時間) 舉行，到時Trump定係Biden贏已經塵埃落定，我哋再燈都唔會改變到結果。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋而家要做嘅唔係望天打卦，而係未雨綢繆，諗定無論邊一方贏咗之後，我哋應該做咩。我哋嘅目標係盡量令到美國反共，我而家諗到嘅行動係趁著美國大選喺twitter向美國人宣傳中共嘅威脅，提醒佢哋要反共。各位巴絲有咩其他意見，請盡快提出，呢次行動由每一個人做搞手，每一個人去行動，我只係想畀一個大綱大家。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先我哋要喺呢幾日討論行動細節同達成共識，之後就請各位文宣巴絲製作<br />\n1.對香港人宣傳本次行動嘅文宣<br />\n2.向美國人宣傳中共嘅威脅嘅文宣(亦都可以循環再用之前啲文宣)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後喺美國大選之前嗰幾日，請全部巴絲一齊喺各大媒介鋪天蓋地式向香港人宣傳呢次行動，號召更多人參加。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(仲記唔記得上年69之前講嘅鋪天蓋地式宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n最後，我哋會喺美國大選結果公佈嘅第二日正式行動。由於美國時間比香港時間遲12小時，所以我計劃喺4/11 20:00(香港時間) 同5/11 10:00(香港時間) ，喺twitter上面宣傳，內容可以係中國嘅威脅、英國指出華為科技威脅英國資訊安全&hellip;，但係我哋要顯得冇咁功利，所以我哋可以先恭喜美國選出新總統，而且我哋要捉住美國人愛國嘅呢個心態，提醒佢哋選咗新總統之後都要全國團結，例如用#AmericansUnited，顯得我哋真心為佢哋好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上全部內容細節都係暫定，邊個都可以提出意見，甚至可以話呢個行動垃圾，直接取消都得，最重要係達成共識，希望巴絲可以集思廣益。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee329bf053f0421cdd9a645c60fe77dc8a22b6f","tid":2243071,"uid":302634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T12:58:56.000Z","msg":"大師兄歸位啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf780e9184a786391ea8ad82300c7186a23bbf73","tid":2243071,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T12:59:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20a9009d30d85a1de924a1d228c5a6dd9c9edad5","tid":2243071,"uid":302634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T12:59:49.000Z","msg":"最重要係達成共識，大家最近好似唔記得咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d55c1d3cd17ad1f695ad6fe7c24d340fc214b87e","tid":2243071,"uid":302634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:00:56.000Z","msg":"做嘢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe862c5a797c8dfd86147909596cb558ace39b5","tid":2243071,"uid":302634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:02:11.000Z","msg":"樓豬推唔推到㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fca979c360cbc5e3d47f00b8848e405899ffc20","tid":2243071,"uid":302634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:03:41.000Z","msg":"再唔做嘢就molamola<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc6e5181d903915734f77537771024118dc4a3e","tid":2243071,"uid":302634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:05:09.000Z","msg":"來人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e104b15215c196c3a023706bcb46c7a30119767","tid":2243071,"uid":302634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:06:30.000Z","msg":"唔好走呀"},{"pid":"8dfedfa9c1476da2ee7e37190a2ba3ba26789c58","tid":2243071,"uid":302634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T13:09:40.000Z","msg":"係咪開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a5ea190fd7a97c12e8cf387324da5d4ce8906a","tid":2243071,"uid":378580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T15:11:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aEcavkV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aEcavkV</a><br />\n#33 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n入去睇下電郵內文，希望對推動香港民主有幫助"},{"pid":"9c7e41e9874a20568b323b202a2552c841b9fd21","tid":2243071,"uid":378580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T15:12:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aEcavkV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aEcavkV</a><br />\n#33 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n入去睇下電郵內文，希望對推動香港民主有幫助"}]}